{
  "texts": [
    "There are still lots of possibilities to develop new Comm-MADRL systems.",
    "Our proposed dimensions encapsulate several aspects of Comm-MADRL, from which we can identify new research directions.",
    "Therefore, we showcase four research directions motivated by leveraging the possible combinations of dimensions and the extensions of corresponding categories.",
    "We also point out further challenges for Comm-MADRL.",
    "Multimodal communicationA versatile robot can hear by sound sensors, read text or talk with human partners."
  ]
}